metadata.name: ZINE AI cover - Tyler
metadata.description:
Meet Tyler, the musician who creates ambient soundscapes using field recordings of natural and industrial sounds. Tyler's next project involves creating a musical instrument that can be played using brain waves. They predict that in the future, music will be a form of telepathy.
✦✦✦
This series of ZINE AI covers is an homage to printed fashion magazines that are almost impossible to imagine without a face on the cover. The ZINE AI covers feature faces generated by AI with the ZINE logo, which is ever-changing. Additionally, each cover story is also generated by AI.
